  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a \u0b8a\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "New circular regarding recruitment of civil servants",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The government has issued a new circular regarding the recruitment of civil servants.",
        "In that regard, the new circular states that heads of government agencies have been empowered to call in the essential and minimum staff required for day-to-day services until further notice."
      ],
